ed="T" n="0880c07"/><persName key="A013736">釋惟則</persName>者，拔俗志高，栖神物表，凡施善務，<lb
ed="T" n="0880c08"/>舉則波隨。常言：「像，是生善之強緣，不得不<lb
ed="T" n="0880c09"/>多立。初之觀也，如對嚴君。次則其心不亂，<lb
ed="T" n="0880c10"/>中則觀門自成。末則如如焉，蕩蕩焉<ptr target="#n3367"/>，三昧安<lb
ed="T" n="0880c11"/>得不現前乎？是以我曹勸化迷俗，得不以<lb
ed="T" n="0880c12"/>此是為先容歟？」由是若雕若塑，形像森然。<lb
ed="T" n="0880c13"/>恒事進修，天邑<ptr type="glossary" target="#g145"/>之間，偏加激勵。屬<persName key="A002120">憲宗</persName>太<lb
ed="T" n="0880c14"/>皇太后<persName key="A019498">郭</persName>氏<date notBefore-iso="+0806-01-29" key="j20154742020967" notAfter-iso="+0821-02-12"><name>元和</name>中</date>為母<persName key="A019499">齊國大長公主</persName>追<lb
ed="T" n="0880c15"/>福，造<placeName key="PL000000042235">奉慈精舍</placeName>，搜擇名德，<persName key="A013736">則</persName>乃預選入居。<lb
ed="T" n="0880c16"/>未久之間，聞<placeName key="PL000000012279"><placeName>四明</placeName><placeName>鄮山</placeName></placeName>有<placeName key="PL000000012309">阿育王塔</placeName>，<date from-iso="+0317-04-07" key="j18369381874651" to-iso="+0420-07-08"><name>東晉</name></date><persName key="A036833">劉<lb
ed="T" n="0880c17"/>薩訶</persName>求現<ptr target="#n3368"/>，往專<anchor xml:id="beg0880sgsz9"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0880sgsz9"/>焉。乃匠意將七寶<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2188"/>為末，<lb
ed="T" n="0880c18"/>用膠範成摹寫脫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2189"/>，酷似。自<placeName key="PL000000012471">甬東</placeName><ptr target="#n3370"/>躬自負歸<lb
ed="T" n="0880c19"/><placeName key="PL000000042235">奉慈寺</placeName>供養，<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京邑</ref>人皆傾瞻歸信焉。</p>
